            <div type="a">
                <column>3</column>
                <head>Handcuffs for Freeman</head>
                <origin>Philadelphia Age</origin>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt>"In going to the polls, remember, freemen, that the Abolitionists of this
                    proud city [Philadelphia] have forged handcuffs for white men, and given
                    shoulder straps to negroes."</excerpt>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>This article from the Philadelphia Age recounts the recent arrest of white
                    men for desertion and notes the irony of white freemen being in shackles while
                    African Americans were being armed for military service.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
